{"tid":852537,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蘋果 (Apple): 沒發現中國間諜晶片","createTime":"2018-10-08T02:29:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-08T09:38:49.000Z","uid":134071,"like":7,"dislike":51,"uniUserReply":54,"replies":[{"pid":"0ba1fa208f3141b1c211cbaf48e7fdb4b67c162f","tid":852537,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T02:29:19.000Z","msg":"被收買?  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n以後唔撚用IPHONE <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20181008/58768996\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181008%2F58768996&d=iI5Tuu4jwIiV0%2BmkkSMa5XadZns4eLIrfSaUqUvMaEw%3D&h=9b86801f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181008%2F58768996&h=68cf4b5a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20181008/58768996</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年10月08日 <br />\n【中美諜戰】蘋果致函參議院　稱沒發現中國間諜晶片<br />\n<br />\n早前有報道指，中國將比米更細小的間諜晶片放入在中國製的電子設備，有指蘋果及亞馬遜等美國巨企中招，惟蘋果公司向美國參議完表示，旗下設備中沒發現中國間諜晶片。<br />\n<br />\n蘋果的保安主管George Stathakopoulos昨日向議院商業委員會致函，表示在重覆檢查報道所指的底板後，沒找到旗下設備有中國間諜晶片。<br />\n<br />\n英國國家網絡保安中心與美國國土安全局指出，沒有理由質疑蘋果與亞馬遜所發出的否認聲明。"},{"pid":"a41c520115d03fc3db533184c004d0c3e710d137","tid":852537,"uid":34140,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T02:35:34.000Z","msg":"沒事兒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65d3b8fcf7611c09df19f86e3cb4ad77d58fbfaf","tid":852537,"uid":22675,"like":64,"dislike":5,"score":59,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T02:38:21.000Z","msg":"咁無就無架啦,想係哋點答你？"},{"pid":"e0b7c1c36e885bc61dc06a41926fa1433543d401","tid":852537,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyT